55.9	Steadicam	Steadicam	Steadicam is a brand of camera stabilizing mount for motion picture cameras that mechanically isolates it from the operator's movement, allowing for a smooth shot even when moving quickly over an uneven surface. Steadicam is now a registered trademark of Tiffen.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/LondonSmog.jpg/220px-LondonSmog.jpg
